---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro'
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro'
import { site } from '../config'
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How PrismApply collects, uses, and protects your profile data, resume, and application packages."
>
  <PageHero
    title="Privacy Policy"
    description={`Last updated: May 27, 2026. This policy describes how ${site.name} handles your data.`}
  />

  <article class="site-container max-w-3xl pb-16 prose-content">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      PrismApply ("we", "us") operates the marketing site at {site.url} and the application at {site.appUrl}.
      We collect information you provide to deliver tailored job application packages. We do not sell your personal data.
    </p>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account data:</strong> email address and hashed password.</li>
      <li><strong>Profile data:</strong> resume text, work history, skills, preferences, and other information you enter in the profile wizard.</li>
      <li><strong>Generated content:</strong> tailored resumes, cover letters, form answers, and match records.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> basic analytics (page views and funnel events) if you consent via our analytics provider.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use your information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Authenticate your account and provide the service.</li>
      <li>Embed your profile for semantic job matching.</li>
      <li>Generate tailored application packages grounded in your profile.</li>
      <li>Improve matching and tailoring quality.</li>
      <li>Communicate service-related updates.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>
      We use infrastructure and API providers (hosting, database, object storage, OpenAI for embeddings and generation, search APIs for job discovery).
      These providers process data on our behalf under their respective terms and security practices.
    </p>

    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>
      We retain your account and profile data while your account is active. You may request deletion by contacting us.
      Some logs may be retained for security and debugging for a limited period.
    </p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>
      Passwords are hashed. API authentication uses HttpOnly cookies. We follow industry-standard practices for transport encryption (HTTPS).
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete your personal data.
      Contact us at privacy@prismapply.com for requests.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy. Material changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
    </p>
  </article>
</PageLayout>
